{
  "info": {
    "name": "1. 🔐 Authentication",
    "description": "Handles identity management, session control, and account recovery. All tokens use JWT. Access tokens expire in 15 minutes; refresh tokens expire in 7 days.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Register",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"johndoe\",\n  \"email\": \"johndoe@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"captcha_token\": \"mock-token\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "register"]
        },
        "description": "## 1. Register User\n\nCreates a new user account. The account remains in a non-verified state until the email confirmation is completed via the verification link sent to the user's inbox.\n\n**Authentication:** Not required\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `username` | String | Yes | Unique, 6-20 characters, alphanumeric and underscores only. |\n| `email` | String | Yes | Valid email format. |\n| `password` | String | Yes | Minimum 8 characters. |\n| `captcha_token` | String | Yes | Captcha verification token. |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "201 Created",
          "status": "Created",
          "code": 201,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"user_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n    \"email\": \"johndoe@example.com\",\n    \"username\": \"johndoe\",\n    \"tier\": \"Free\",\n    \"message\": \"Registration successful. Please check your email to verify.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Invalid CAPTCHA",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Invalid CAPTCHA token.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "409 Conflict – Email/Username Taken",
          "status": "Conflict",
          "code": 409,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Email or username already exists.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Login",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Check if the request was successful\r",
              "if (pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {\r",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();\r",
              "    \r",
              "    // Automatically save the Access Token\r",
              "    if (jsonData.access_token) {\r",
              "        pm.environment.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.access_token);\r",
              "        console.log(\"Access Token updated!\");\r",
              "    }\r",
              "    \r",
              "    // Automatically save the Refresh Token\r",
              "    if (jsonData.refresh_token) {\r",
              "        pm.environment.set(\"refreshToken\", jsonData.refresh_token);\r",
              "        console.log(\"Refresh Token updated!\");\r",
              "    }\r",
              "    \r",
              "    // Automatically save the User ID\r",
              "    if (jsonData.user && jsonData.user.user_id) {\r",
              "        pm.environment.set(\"user_id\", jsonData.user.user_id);\r",
              "        console.log(\"User ID updated!\");\r",
              "    }\r",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"johndoe@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "login"]
        },
        "description": "## 2. Login User\n\nExchanges user credentials for access and refresh tokens. On success, the test script automatically saves `accessToken`, `refreshToken`, and `user_id` to the Postman environment.\n\n**Authentication:** Not required\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `email` | String | Yes | Registered email. |\n| `password` | String | Yes | Account password. |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1Ni...\",\n    \"refresh_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1Ni...\",\n    \"user\": {\n        \"user_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n        \"username\": \"johndoe\",\n        \"email\": \"johndoe@example.com\",\n        \"display_name\": \"johndoe\",\n        \"tier\": \"Free\",\n        \"avatar_url\": \"avatar-url.png\"\n    }\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Missing Fields",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Bad Request: Email and password are required.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "401 Unauthorized – Invalid Credentials",
          "status": "Unauthorized",
          "code": 401,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Invalid credentials.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "403 Forbidden – Suspended Account",
          "status": "Forbidden",
          "code": 403,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Forbidden: Suspended account.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Verify Email",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "verify-email"]
        },
        "description": "## 3. Verify Email\n\nVerifies the user's email address using the JWT token sent upon registration. Once verified, the user can fully access all platform features.\n\n**Authentication:** Not required\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `token` | String | Yes | Verification JWT from the email link. |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK – Verified",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Email successfully verified.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "200 OK – Already Verified",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Email is already verified.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Missing Token",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Token is required.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Invalid/Expired Token",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Invalid or expired verification token.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "404 Not Found – User Not Found",
          "status": "Not Found",
          "code": 404,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"User not found.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Resend Verification",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"johndoe@example.com\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/resend-verification",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "resend-verification"]
        },
        "description": "## 4. Resend Verification Email\n\nResends the verification email with a new JWT token if the previous one expired or was lost. Fails if the user is already verified.\n\n**Authentication:** Not required\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `email` | String | Yes | Registered email address. |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK – Email Sent",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"message\": \"A new verification email has been sent. Please check your inbox.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "200 OK – User Not Found (Security Fallback)",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"message\": \"If that email is registered, a new verification link has been sent.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Missing Email",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Email is required.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Already Verified",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"This account is already verified. Please log in.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Refresh Token",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"dGhpcyBpcyBhIHJlZnJlc2ggdG9rZW4...\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "refresh"]
        },
        "description": "## 5. Refresh Token\n\nGenerates a new pair of access and refresh tokens using a valid refresh token. Use this to keep the user's session alive without forcing a re-login.\n\n**Authentication:** Not required (uses refresh token in body)\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `refresh_token` | String | Yes | Valid refresh token from login. |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs_new...\",\n    \"refresh_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs_new...\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Missing Refresh Token",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Refresh token is required.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "401 Unauthorized – Invalid/Expired Refresh Token",
          "status": "Unauthorized",
          "code": 401,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Invalid or expired refresh token. Please log in again.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "403 Forbidden – Suspended Account",
          "status": "Forbidden",
          "code": 403,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Forbidden: Suspended account.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "404 Not Found – User Not Found",
          "status": "Not Found",
          "code": 404,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"User not found.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "6. Forgot Password",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"johndoe@example.com\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "forgot-password"]
        },
        "description": "## 6. Forgot Password\n\nInitiates the password reset flow. Sends a reset link to the email provided. For security, this endpoint always returns the same message regardless of whether the email exists in the database.\n\n**Authentication:** Not required\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `email` | String | Yes | Registered email address. |\n\n### Security Note\n\nThe response is intentionally identical for both existing and non-existing emails to prevent email enumeration attacks."
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK – Email Exists (Reset Link Sent)",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"message\": \"If that email address is in our database, we will send you a link to reset your password.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "200 OK – Email Does Not Exist (Same Response)",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"message\": \"If that email address is in our database, we will send you a link to reset your password.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Missing Email",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Email is required.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "7. Reset Password",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"reset-token-from-email\",\n  \"new_password\": \"NewSecurePass456!\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "reset-password"]
        },
        "description": "## 7. Reset Password\n\nApplies a new password using the reset token sent via email. The token is single-use and expires after 1 hour.\n\n**Authentication:** Not required\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `token` | String | Yes | Reset token from the email link. |\n| `new_password` | String | Yes | The new secure password (min 8 chars). |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Password has been successfully reset. You can now log in.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Missing Fields",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Token and new_password are required.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Invalid/Expired Token",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Invalid or expired password reset token.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "8. Logout",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"dGhpcyBpcyBhIHJlZnJlc2ggdG9rZW4...\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "logout"]
        },
        "description": "## 8. Logout\n\nInvalidates the user's refresh token on the server, ending the session. The access token will naturally expire but cannot be used to generate new tokens after logout.\n\n**Authentication:** Required\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `refresh_token` | String | Yes | Active refresh token to be cleared. |\n\n### Note\n\nLogout is idempotent — if the refresh token is already invalid or belongs to no user, the endpoint still returns 200 OK."
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Logged out successfully.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Missing Refresh Token",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Refresh token is required.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "401 Unauthorized – No Access Token",
          "status": "Unauthorized",
          "code": 401,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"You are not logged in. Please log in to get access.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "9. Social Login (Dynamic)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Automatically save tokens upon successful social login\r",
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {\r",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();\r",
              "    if (jsonData.access_token) pm.environment.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.access_token);\r",
              "    if (jsonData.refresh_token) pm.environment.set(\"refreshToken\", jsonData.refresh_token);\r",
              "    if (jsonData.user && jsonData.user.user_id) pm.environment.set(\"user_id\", jsonData.user.user_id);\r",
              "    console.log(\"Social session tokens saved to environment!\");\r",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"<PASTE_SOCIAL_TOKEN_HERE>\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/social/:provider",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "social", ":provider"],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "provider",
              "value": "google",
              "description": "Options: google, facebook, apple"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "## 9. Social Login / Registration\n\nA unified endpoint for Google, Facebook, and Apple. If the user does not exist, they are automatically registered. If they do exist, they are logged in.\n\n**Authentication:** Not required (uses Provider Token)\n\n### Path Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `provider` | The social platform (`google`, `facebook`, or `apple`). |\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| `token` | String | The JWT or Access Token received from the social provider's SDK. |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK - Successful Social Auth",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1Ni...\",\n    \"refresh_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1Ni...\",\n    \"user\": {\n        \"user_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n        \"username\": \"google_user_1234\",\n        \"email\": \"user@gmail.com\",\n        \"display_name\": \"John Doe\",\n        \"tier\": \"Free\"\n    }\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request - Missing Token",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Token is required.\"\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "401 Unauthorized - Invalid Provider Token",
          "status": "Unauthorized",
          "code": 401,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Invalid Google ID token.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
